Description: XIVO Phones and Cards Firmwares Fetch Engine
 XIVO is a system based on a powerful IPBX, to bring an easy to
 install solution for telephony and related services.
 .
 This package contains the engine used to fetch the necessary
 firmwares for XIVO IP phones and cards.
